SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]

    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]

) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]

LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [p0].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Brand], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[StockQuantity], [t].[Id0], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[Name0], [t0].[Id], [t0].[DiscountId], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StartDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t0].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name] AS [Name0]

    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]

LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Brand], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[StockQuantity], [t].[Id0], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[Name0], [t0].[Id], [t0].[DiscountId], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StartDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]

    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]

) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]

) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[Name], [d].[StartDate]
FROM [Discounts] AS [d]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d0]
    WHERE [d].[Id] = [d0].[DiscountId] AND [d0].[ProductId] = @__id_0)
2025-06-18 11:43:12.885 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]
2025-06-18 11:43:12.886 +04:00 [INF] Retrieved all discounts for product with ID 12 successfully.
2025-06-18 11:43:12.886 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Brand], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[StockQuantity], [t].[Id0], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[Name0], [t0].[Id], [t0].[DiscountId], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StartDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Discounts] AS [d]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d0]
    WHERE [d].[Id] = [d0].[DiscountId] AND [d0].[ProductId] = @__id_0)
2025-06-18 12:00:22.927 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]

    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]

) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

2025-06-18 12:02:08.661 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

2025-06-18 12:03:39.591 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

2025-06-18 12:05:38.060 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

2025-06-18 12:07:15.631 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]

    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]

) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[MainImage], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Name], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Value], [c].[ImageUrl], [c].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[DiscountId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[DiscountPercentage], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Name], [t].[StartDate]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductFeatures] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[DiscountId], [d].[ProductId], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[DiscountPercentage], [d0].[EndDate], [d0].[Name], [d0].[StartDate]
    FROM [DiscountProducts] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d0] ON [d].[DiscountId] = [d0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id], [t].[Id]
